OL,6,FStudents at a school in are
OL,7,Fcollectively speaking 25 different
OL,8,Flanguages - making it one of the most
OL,9,Fculturally diverse schools in the
OL,10,Fisland.
OL,12,FNotre Dame de Rosaire Primary School
OL,13,Fin St Peter Port caters for children
OL,14,Fwho speak languages such as Polish,
OL,15,FArabic and Portuguese.
OL,17,FHead Mary Robertshaw has been teaching
OL,18,Fin the island for two decades.
