OL,3,CMore than half of students at Guernsey
OL,4,Cschool speak an additional language
OL,6,FShe said: "Guernsey has changed
OL,7,Fmassively. Five years ago about 25-30%
OL,8,Fof pupils had English as an additional
OL,9,Flanguage, now it's about 55%. Over
OL,10,Fhalf of our children speak another
OL,11,Flanguage and in some classes that's up
OL,12,Fto 70 per cent, so it's changed hugely
OL,13,Fand for the better.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G2/6
