OL,3,CMore than half of students at Guernsey
OL,4,Cschool speak an additional language
OL,6,FThe change over recent years is
OL,7,Fbelieved to be due to the relaxation
OL,8,Fof the island's population rules with
OL,9,Ffamilies relocating from places such
OL,10,Fas the Philippines, the Democratic
OL,11,FRepublic of the Congo and Poland.
OL,13,FRebecca Le Marre teaches the school's
OL,14,Freception class and says it is
OL,15,Ffulfilling to work in such a diverse
OL,16,Fplace.
