OL,3,CMore than half of students at Guernsey
OL,4,Cschool speak an additional language
OL,6,FShe explained: "It's got a very
OL,7,Fdifferent feel to it than other
OL,8,Fclasses I've worked with in the
OL,9,Fisland, but it's so rewarding because
OL,10,Fyou have children that come in and you
OL,11,Fsee them interact, particularly in
OL,12,Fearly years when we have our
OL,13,Fconstructive play."
OL,15,FIt is not just the children who are
OL,16,Flearning new languages, Rebecca says
OL,17,Fthe parents are learning too.
