OL,3,CMore than half of students at Guernsey
OL,4,Cschool speak an additional language
OL,6,FShe added: "A lot of parents here are
OL,7,Flearning English themselves and it's
OL,8,Famazing to get feedback from them as
OL,9,Ftheir child is doing phonics, learning
OL,10,Fto read, that's improving their
OL,11,FEnglish at home.
OL,13,F"I had a parent tell me that their
OL,14,FEnglish is improving so much because
OL,15,Ftheir son is correcting them and
OL,16,Fhelping them to learn how to speak
OL,17,FEnglish more fluently and that's
OL,18,Famazing!"
